  "publishedAt": "2026-06-03T15:12:34.000Z",
  "contentHtml": "<h2>The lost art of building cities</h2>\n<p><span>In the nineteenth century, cities often grew a thousandfold while increasing wages, the size of homes, and delivering great public goods like electricity and plumbing to their people. What made them so extraordinary? They had a hybrid of laissez-faire and top-down control. Landowners could build almost anything they liked but street networks were laid out with near-Soviet thoroughness decades in advance. Transport and utilities, meanwhile, ran as regulated monopolies. They were funded by users, turned a profit, but prices were controlled.</span><br><br><span>Samuel, Ben and Aria discuss what made this system work and why it was dismantled.</span></p>\n<p><span>You can also watch the rest of the episode on </span><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/the-lost-art-of-building-cities/id1819488714?i=1000770945140\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Apple Podcasts</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/3Mkf9ax0YL8o2t6pcqPHIg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spotify</a><span>, and </span><a href=\"https://youtu.be/OINr7uJDjOg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YouTube</a><span>.</span></p>\n<h4>Discussion about this video</h4>\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LfEW!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F198328291%2Fc9b44f53-bb47-4cb2-b790-983272012d7a%2Ftranscoded-1779184335.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!6gYu!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F194995216%2F92ddb8f2-8c3a-4002-a6db-10cd2815f76e%2Ftranscoded-1776834204.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!8bZN!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F193498238%2Fd59bbb03-1c65-4db7-80f9-0c21f0bac321%2Ftranscoded-1775634249.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!vV06!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F192008453%2F71ea4ebe-3bdc-4dbb-93c4-570ac597c729%2Ftranscoded-1774389865.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!p1ys!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F189009804%2Ff8271cba-5e31-48c6-a9fe-11c0c046b6b1%2Ftranscoded-1772029800.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!tN-J!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F186304896%2Fece58b60-3298-40d8-9672-1fb5f84a3c6d%2Ftranscoded-1769789746.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!S9Yr!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F178147967%2Fde201865-9f55-42c9-99ea-cde538f11df4%2Ftranscoded-1762425112.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">",
